---
title: Rosemary Roasted Chicken and Grapes with Creamy Cauliflower Mash
description: Rich and flavourful rosemary chicken is perfectly paired with juicy blistered grapes and creamy cauliflower mashed potatoes. It has all the flair of a Sunday supper, but perfect for any day of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rosemary-roasted-chicken-and-grapes-d8e2a51d.jpg
